{"tid":1516253,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「認真討論」點解我地要抵制大家樂唔抵制大快活？","createTime":"2019-08-29T13:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T03:24:08.000Z","uid":273889,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dadd78abb2da4f8fdf000581d083296a6936d2c2","tid":1516253,"uid":273889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:30:48.000Z","msg":"事緣我尋日唔小心食左餐米線陣（大家樂集團）<br />\n<br />\n唺然後先諗起要抵制<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係諗諗下大家樂好似冇出過黎鬧示威者喎<br />\n咁就search下做乜要抵制佢，然後發現左一樣野：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家樂與香港同類快餐店大快活的創辦人分別是羅騰祥及羅芳祥，同為維他奶創辦人羅桂祥的弟弟。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原來大家樂同大快活（仲有維他奶係一家人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想問抵制大家樂係咪因為佢地提供狗飼料？<br />\n仲有冇原因？<br />\n駛唔駛抵制埋大快活維他奶？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c98ab8073d8efc88b367008c0ba0bddb200f6b6","tid":1516253,"uid":273889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:31:12.000Z","msg":"我要食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c73cf0656ee3b01575742dea515774be7c02f3","tid":1516253,"uid":273889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:33:07.000Z","msg":"我要食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba884ceae1c5b307bc21cced31bb72315a79f13a","tid":1516253,"uid":295662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c98ab8073d8efc88b367008c0ba0bddb200f6b6","tid":1516253,"uid":273889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:31:12.000Z","msg":"我要食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:38:54.000Z","msg":"你冇野可以食了<br />\n返屋企食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc0b1842fca2f81c4edb388869c6512c8430fca7","tid":1516253,"uid":273889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba884ceae1c5b307bc21cced31bb72315a79f13a","tid":1516253,"uid":295662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c98ab8073d8efc88b367008c0ba0bddb200f6b6","tid":1516253,"uid":273889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:31:12.000Z","msg":"我要食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:38:54.000Z","msg":"你冇野可以食了<br />\n返屋企食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:59:57.000Z","msg":"快餐店好似得返雞上校？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e67cda6049327cdeff1a8554b588bd0f3a1f9b","tid":1516253,"uid":231818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T14:27:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqBOnuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqBOnuf.jpg&h=a519857e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環球時報總編輯胡錫進尼左香港<br />\n佢話會去示威現場<br />\n同青年對話<br />\n佢對話完<br />\n係大陸人眼中實更有權威<br />\n到時輸出革命會更難<br />\n<br />\n建議大家係佢落場時<br />\n準備定中共啲衰野<br />\n同一定要影住佢<br />\n錄低佢up過啲咩"},{"pid":"2821544aa6f52e427a215fe49d5eaad44c17f557","tid":1516253,"uid":295662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc0b1842fca2f81c4edb388869c6512c8430fca7","tid":1516253,"uid":273889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba884ceae1c5b307bc21cced31bb72315a79f13a","tid":1516253,"uid":295662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c98ab8073d8efc88b367008c0ba0bddb200f6b6","tid":1516253,"uid":273889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:31:1